      "source": [
        "# Advanced Extractive Text Summarization with TextRank\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Domain:** Natural Language Processing (NLP) · Text Mining · Unsupervised Learning\n",
        "\n",
        "## Learning Objectives\n",
        "\n",
        "- Understand the TextRank algorithm for extractive summarization\n",
        "- Work with a real-world summarization dataset (CNN/DailyMail)\n",
        "- Implement proper data loading and preprocessing pipelines\n",
        "- Evaluate summaries using automatic metrics (ROUGE)\n",
        "- Compare different extractive summarization approaches\n",
        "\n",
        "## 🎯 Business Context\n",
        "\n",
        "In today's information-rich world, the ability to quickly extract key insights from documents is crucial. Extractive summarization algorithms identify the most important sentences in a document and combine them to create a concise summary. This technique is particularly valuable for:\n",
        "\n",
        "- **Research analysts** digesting lengthy reports\n",
        "- **Journalists** summarizing news articles\n",
        "- **Students** reviewing academic papers\n",
        "- **Business professionals** processing documents efficiently\n",
        "\n",
        "## 📊 Dataset: CNN/DailyMail\n",
        "\n",
        "We'll be using the CNN/DailyMail dataset, a standard benchmark for text summarization containing news articles and their corresponding highlights/summaries. This dataset provides:\n",
        "\n",
        "- **Real-world content**: News articles from CNN and the Daily Mail\n",
        "- **Reference summaries**: Professional highlights for each article\n",
        "- **Diverse topics**: Politics, business, technology, entertainment, and more\n",
        "- **Standard evaluation**: Enables comparison with state-of-the-art methods\n",
        "\n",
        "### Dataset Statistics\n",
        "\n",
        "- **Articles**: ~287,000 (we'll use a small sample for learning)\n",
        "- **Average article length**: ~800 words\n",
        "- **Average summary length**: ~60 words\n",
        "- **Format**: JSON with 'article' and 'highlights' fields\n"
      ]
    },
    {
