      "source": [
        "## 9. Conclusion and Further Learning\n",
        "\n",
        "### Summary of Achievements\n",
        "\n",
        "1. ✅ **New Dataset**: Successfully loaded and explored the CNN/DailyMail dataset\n",
        "2. ✅ **Enhanced Preprocessing**: Implemented advanced cleaning, lemmatization, and stop word removal\n",
        "3. ✅ **TextRank Implementation**: Built a graph-based extractive summarizer\n",
        "4. ✅ **Evaluation Framework**: Added automatic ROUGE scoring for objective comparison\n",
        "5. ✅ **Method Comparison**: Benchmarked TextRank against the original frequency-based method\n",
        "\n",
        "### Key Learnings\n",
        "\n",
        "- **TextRank** uses sentence similarity to build a graph and PageRank to find important sentences\n",
